title: NHS activity and capacity during the coronavirus (COVID-19) pandemic
description:
Statistics on coronavirus: 
cases
deaths
hospitalisations
new admissions to hospital
invasive ventilated beds in Wales
general and acute beds use in Wales
ambulance calls
111 and NHS Direct calls
daily A&E attendances
NHS staff absences
They have been published to provide latest data. The statistics will be used by the NHS Chief Executive in his weekly press conference.
datasetNotes: On landing page scroll down to latest release link. On new page dataset can be found towards bottom of page under heading "Data".
sizingNotes: Several tabs with simple table structures. Multiple dimensions and sub-dimensions. Some footnotes.
